subject: Handwriting practice guides

messageBody:
For those of us who need more QS Junior handwriting practice and like
the look of the Thoth font, I've created some guides showing each
letter written in between guides, and with guides below in which the
letter can be copied.

I've uploaded them in to the files section (in the Practice folder),
along with some extra practice material.

--Sergey
